Southmark Corp said shareholders will beissued, as a special dividend, rights to acquire 22 shares ofAmerican Realty Trust &lt;ARB> for each 100 shares of Southmarkowned.    The record date for Southmark shareholders to receive theserights will be May one with an ex-dividend date of April 27.    Southmark received these rights on April six, as the holderof about 84 pct of American Realty Trust's outstanding shares.    Reuter&#3;